<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakavatsarē kṣitisamudrārkkāṁkitē mādhavē kṛṣṇē śaṁbhutithau budhasya
<lb n="2"/>divasē śrīmānṛsiṁhāgrataḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmadgaṁggadharādhināthamahiṣī śrīlakṣmidēvī sva
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yaṁ prādāddīpamakhaṁḍamuttamagavāṁ paṁccāśatā susthiraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakava
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ruṣaṁbulu 1241 gunēṁṭi śrīdēvādidēva śrī jagannāthadēvarala vijayarājyasaṁ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vatsaraṁbulu 13 śrāhi riṣabha kṛṣṇa 11 yu paṁḍitavāramunāṁḍu śaṁkkara
<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>dāsu</unclear> mahāsēnāpati Adhikāramuna jaṁttaṟunāṁṭi pratāpagaṁggarājula ma
<lb n="7" break="no"/>hādēvi lakṣmīdēvigāru śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sannidhi nityamunnu veluṁguṭaku peṭṭi
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>na</unclear> Akhaṁḍḍadīpamu Okkaṁṭi mōdālu 51 Ī dīpapratima 1
<lb n="9"/>I dharmmuvu ĀcaṁdrārkkasthāĪgā calla
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁgaladu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> pā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lanīyyō manīṣibhiḥ śatrurēva hi
<lb n="12"/>śatru<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> syādharmma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śatru<unclear>rna</unclear> kasyacit
<lb n="13"/>I dharmmupu śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

